Username is "grrcupcake" if you want to find me.

Exams-done.
Semester-over.
YAYAYAYAY!

Now the next two weeks will involve Jeff, sleep, the beach and other random times dancing, writing, or generally being drunk as hell. 

Then summer session starts, which will be amazingly amazing ONLY! because I get to spend many hours deciphering common denominators with the ever lovely Diana Hurlburt :)

Things are looking up :0)
